data.description: This is the one!! This beautiful 3 bedroom and 2-bathroom Home is located in the heart of Brandon. Once you get through the front door you will immediately notice the living and dining room a wide and open feeling. The Master suite has on suite bathroom with shower. The two other bedrooms are on the other side of the house and share a nice, remodeled bathroom with bathtub. Everything has been remodeled or exchanged. Kitchen appliances cabinets 2021, Roof 2011, Brand NEW A/C 2023.This property has a perfect location to cover all your needs. A Few Miles for access to I-75, Malls, Restaurants, New Hospital, DMV, Movie Theater, Florida Fair Ground, Beaches, Busch Gardens and more Don't miss this opportunity to enjoy Fl lifestyle. Make your appointment today.
